    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s super reliable and ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved, carefully maintained, and runs like an absolute dream! It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for someone new to take the wheel. Whether you're commuting or hitting the road for the weekend, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
