    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of a well-maintained driver's car. The exterior paint still holds a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you'll find typical minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scratch near the driver-side door handle. The interior is exceptionally clean; the upholstery is free of tears or stains, though the driver\u2019s seat bolster shows the light softening expected from regular use. All electronic features, including the climate control, infotainment system, and power windows, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in great shape with a consistent service history\u2014recent work includes a fresh oil change and a brake inspection. The engine runs quietly, the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life left. This is a reliable, honest car that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
